---

<section id="about" class="about">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">About Us</h2>

    <div class="about-content">
      <div class="about-text">
        <p class="about-lead">
          Endurance Protection Group is an operator group dedicated to acquiring and operating independent property & casualty insurance agencies across Texas.
        </p>

        <p>
          We believe in the enduring value of relationship-driven insurance businesses. Our approach is rooted in long-term stewardship—we acquire agencies with the intention of operating them for decades, not flipping them for quick returns.
        </p>

        <p>
          Founded in Austin, Texas, we understand the unique character of Texas communities and the important role that local insurance agencies play in protecting families and businesses. We seek to preserve this legacy while bringing operational excellence and growth capital to the agencies we partner with.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="about-values">
        <div class="value-item">
          <h3>Long-Term Focus</h3>
          <p>We acquire to operate, not to flip. Our commitment extends for generations.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="value-item">
          <h3>Operator-Led</h3>
          <p>Hands-on management with deep industry expertise and operational know-how.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="value-item">
          <h3>Texas Roots</h3>
          <p>Proudly based in Austin, serving communities across the Lone Star State.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    background: #ffffff;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    color: #1a1a2e;
  }

  .about-content {
    display: grid;
    gap: 4rem;
  }

  .about-text {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .about-lead {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: #1a1a2e;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .about-text p {
    color: #5a5a6e;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .about-text p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .about-values {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .value-item {
    padding: 2rem;
    background: #f8f9fa;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
  }

  .value-item h3 {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: #1a1a2e;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .value-item p {
    color: #5a5a6e;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
  }
</style>
